---
description: Repo-wide AI use policy and working conventions
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow @AI_POLICY.md and @CLAUDE.md for all work in this repo — they are binding operating rules, not suggestions. In particular: never force-push, rewrite history, or resolve a merge conflict without the user reviewing the result first, and never call the GitHub API/`gh` CLI or any GitHub-connected tool to read or act on issues, PR comments, or history on your own.
